{"_id":"zqtdybsbvvq","ownership":{"default":0},"_stats":{"compendiumSource":null,"duplicateSource":null,"exportSource":null,"coreVersion":"13.350","systemId":"mutants-and-masterminds-3e","systemVersion":"1.39.13"},"name":"Easily Removable","type":"modificateur","img":"systems/mutants-and-masterminds-3e/assets/icons/pouvoir.svg","system":{"type":"defaut","description":"<p>An easily removable power can be taken away with a disarm or grab action. The flaw is worth –2 points per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -2 points per 5 points.</p>","notes":"<p>An easily removable power can be taken away with a disarm or grab action. The flaw is worth –2 points per 5 total power points.</p><p>Flat -2 points per 5 points.</p>","cout":{"fixe":true,"rang":false,"value":-2}}}